  "description": "Hyperion Seraph shotgun firing slow gyrojet pellets. Each pellet quickly splits into three: a centre pellet continues straight while two side pellets arc outward, then curve back and vanish when they rejoin.\n\nBest at mid-range where all three paths connect; weak up close due to wide spread and at long range where the side pellets disappear. Slow projectiles struggle versus fast or airborne targets, but at the right distance it hits extremely hard on large enemies and bosses, and the curved paths can repeatedly trigger Zer0's B0re.",
