    "title": "Because it enters your face. Get it? IT ENTERS YOUR FACE!",
    "description": "+60 percent critical hit damage (scales).\nConsumes 2 ammo per shot.\nSlow pellets; each splits into two extra pellets after a short distance. Side pellets arc left and right, then curve back to the centre pellet and vanish on contact.\nNo movement speed penalty while aiming.\nHyperion: sustained fire increases accuracy and reduces recoil."
  },
  "notes": "Never spawns with a scope.\nNo aim-walk slowdown comes from using the NULL scope part (not Scope_None); forcing NULL on other guns gives the same effect.\nOnly Interfacer and Greed can roll with NULL.\nWith enough Expertise, Axton can move faster than sprint speed while aiming, especially with a Legendary Soldier class mod.",
